<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.1">
<l>piṉṉai maṇāḷaṉaip pēril kiṭantāṉai</l>
<l>muṉṉai yamarar mutaltaṉi vittiṉai</l>
<l>yeṉṉai yumeṅkaḷ kuṭimuḻu tāṭkoṇṭa</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉai vantukuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="Indent">mātavaṉ taṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come to the husband of Pinnai, the one who reclines in Per,</l>
<l>the sole cause, the first of the ancient celestials,</l>
<l>the king who took in service our whole lineage, including me,</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb [his] curly locks!</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly locks of Madhava!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
